From Ed Hamrick Subject Re PD code for crypt like encryption In article A Jerry Natowitz writes I am looking for some Public Domain and exportable code for encryption Nothing elaborate, just something that will satisfy a marketing need Oh yes, UNIX platform You can find what you're looking for on hundreds of sites worldwide Try anonymous ftp to nic funet fi Finland pub unix bsd net lib libc gen crypt c Z This includes source code for fully functional DES encryption and decryption There are some who believe that public domain code is exportable, some who don't Make your own judgements, but it seems obvious to me Regards, Ed Hamrick